%% Clarity (todo-app) -- Data Flow Diagram
%% Shows the flow of data through all layers for a typical task creation

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Angular SPA<br/>(Component)
    participant Store as NgRx Store<br/>(Effect)
    participant HTTP as TaskService<br/>(HTTP Client)
    participant Ctrl as TaskController<br/>(API Layer)
    participant AppSvc as TaskApplicationService<br/>(Application Layer)
    participant Agg as Task Aggregate<br/>(Domain Layer)
    participant Repo as JpaTaskRepository<br/>(Infrastructure)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Cache as Redis

    Note over User,Cache: CREATE TASK FLOW

    User->>UI: Click "Add Task", type title, press Enter
    UI->>Store: Dispatch CreateTask action
    Store->>Store: Reducer: add task optimistically<br/>(pending state)
    Store->>HTTP: Effect: call taskService.create()
    HTTP->>Ctrl: POST /api/v1/tasks<br/>{ title, listId, priority }
    Ctrl->>Ctrl: @Valid: validate CreateTaskRequest DTO
    Ctrl->>AppSvc: createTask(CreateTaskCommand)
    AppSvc->>Agg: Task.create(title, listId, priority, userId)
    Agg->>Agg: Enforce invariants:<br/>- title not blank<br/>- title <= 255 chars<br/>- valid priority
    Agg-->>AppSvc: Return Task + TaskCreatedEvent
    AppSvc->>Repo: taskRepository.save(task)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO tasks (...)
    DB-->>Repo: Confirm insert
    AppSvc->>Cache: Invalidate cache keys:<br/>cache:tasks:user:{userId}:*<br/>cache:today:user:{userId}<br/>cache:counts:user:{userId}
    Cache-->>AppSvc: OK
    AppSvc-->>Ctrl: Return TaskResponse DTO
    Ctrl-->>HTTP: 201 Created { task }
    HTTP-->>Store: Effect: dispatch CreateTaskSuccess
    Store->>Store: Reducer: replace optimistic task<br/>with server-confirmed task
    Store-->>UI: Selector emits updated task list
    UI-->>User: Task appears in list<br/>(already visible from optimistic update)

    Note over User,Cache: READ TASKS FLOW (Cache Hit)

    User->>UI: Navigate to task list
    UI->>Store: Dispatch LoadTasks action
    Store->>HTTP: Effect: call taskService.getByList(listId)
    HTTP->>Ctrl: GET /api/v1/tasks?listId={id}
    Ctrl->>AppSvc: getTasks(TaskQuery)
    AppSvc->>Cache: Check cache:tasks:user:{userId}:list:{listId}
    Cache-->>AppSvc: CACHE HIT: return cached tasks
    AppSvc-->>Ctrl: Return List of TaskResponse
    Ctrl-->>HTTP: 200 OK { tasks[] }
    HTTP-->>Store: Effect: dispatch LoadTasksSuccess
    Store->>Store: Reducer: set tasks in state
    Store-->>UI: Selector emits task list
    UI-->>User: Render task list

    Note over User,Cache: READ TASKS FLOW (Cache Miss)

    User->>UI: Navigate to different list
    UI->>Store: Dispatch LoadTasks action
    Store->>HTTP: Effect: call taskService.getByList(listId)
    HTTP->>Ctrl: GET /api/v1/tasks?listId={id}
    Ctrl->>AppSvc: getTasks(TaskQuery)
    AppSvc->>Cache: Check cache:tasks:user:{userId}:list:{listId}
    Cache-->>AppSvc: CACHE MISS
    AppSvc->>Repo: taskRepository.findByUserAndList(userId, listId)
    Repo->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE ...
    DB-->>Repo: Return result set
    Repo-->>AppSvc: Return List of Task
    AppSvc->>Cache: SET cache:tasks:user:{userId}:list:{listId}<br/>TTL=5min
    Cache-->>AppSvc: OK
    AppSvc-->>Ctrl: Return List of TaskResponse
    Ctrl-->>HTTP: 200 OK { tasks[] }
    HTTP-->>Store: Effect: dispatch LoadTasksSuccess
    Store-->>UI: Render task list
    UI-->>User: Display tasks
